<i>You'll become monkeys when I order you to!</i>

11
00:00:37,037 --> 00:00:38,121
<i>Humor me as you hunch over</i>

12
00:00:38,204 --> 00:00:40,081
<i>-and rub your hands!</i>
-You're exactly right.

13
00:00:40,165 --> 00:00:42,792
<i>-Never stop singing my praises!</i>
-You're the greatest, milord.

14
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:43,960
