15
00:00:44,043 --> 00:00:46,171
{\an8}<i>Let me say it one more time.</i>

16
00:00:46,254 --> 00:00:48,381
{\an8}<i>I am a god!</i>

17
00:00:52,051 --> 00:00:54,471
<i>This guy is a complete weirdo.</i>

18
00:00:56,306 --> 00:00:59,893
What exactly is your domain as a god?

19
00:00:59,976 --> 00:01:02,687
<i>Why are you falling for his lies?</i>

20
00:01:03,229 --> 00:01:04,981
-Good question.
<i>-What?</i>

21
00:01:05,065 --> 00:01:06,816
You're a sharp kid.

22
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:10,028
<i>That was a dumb question.
Which part of it was sharp?</i>

23
00:01:10,695 --> 00:01:14,991
{\an8}I am a god who rules over flamboyance,
the God of Festivals.

24
00:01:15,617 --> 00:01:16,701
<i>He's an idiot.</i>

25
00:01:16,785 --> 00:01:19,829
<i>He must be ruling over idiots.</i>

26
00:01:20,622 --> 00:01:22,624
I'm the King of the Mountains.

27
00:01:22,707 --> 00:01:25,585
Nice to meet you, God of Festivals.

28
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:31,174
What are you on about?

29
00:01:31,758 --> 00:01:33,885
You're weirding me out.

30
00:01:36,137 --> 00:01:38,807
{\an8}<i>Hold up! You were acting just like him!</i>

31
00:01:38,890 --> 00:01:40,642
{\an8}<i>You're just as cringey!</i>

32
00:01:40,725 --> 00:01:44,229
-What? What did you say?
-Inosuke, don't!

33
00:01:44,312 --> 00:01:46,105
-You're creepy.
-Let me go, Gonpachiro!

34
00:01:46,189 --> 00:01:50,568
<i>I suppose even he can't stand people
who are as delusional as himself.</i>

35
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:54,239
We don't have all day.

36
00:01:54,322 --> 00:01:55,365
Let's get going.

37
00:01:56,407 --> 00:01:57,534
Keep up with me.

38
00:02:03,373 --> 00:02:04,249
What?

39
00:02:04,332 --> 00:02:05,291
He's gone!

40
